{"word":"G102 - ἀδύνατος - adýnatos - ad-oo'-nat-os - Could not do","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδύνατος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">adýnatos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ad-oo'-nat-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Could not do</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கூடாத, வழங்காத, செய்யக்கூடாத, பலவீனங்கள் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without strength, impotent, impossible"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1415 - δυνατός - dynatós - doo-nat-os'/1415\">G1415</a>; <i>unable</i>, that is, <i>weak</i> (literally or figuratively); passively <i>impossible:</i> - could not do, impossible, impotent, not possible, weak.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G101/101\">G101</a>, <a href=\"#/G102/102\">G102</a>, <a href=\"#/G1410/1410\">G1410</a>, <a href=\"#/G1411/1411\">G1411</a>, <a href=\"#/G1412/1412\">G1412</a>, <a href=\"#/G1413/1413\">G1413</a>, <a href=\"#/G1414/1414\">G1414</a>, <a href=\"#/G1415/1415\">G1415</a>, <a href=\"#/G1743/1743\">G1743</a>"}]}